des:
You can ask Wellness Daily for tips that can help you streamline your wellness goals. Wellness Daily is your daily companion on your journey to greater wellness and health.

Now there are no excuses for not being well!!

Disclaimer:The tips are sourced from free web content published by Healthfinder (U.S. Department of Health and Human Services). 
The skill is not produced by or affiliated with any U.S. Federal agencies.
The information provided in this skill is not intended to be a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
